Chile’s Cencosud to Open 25 Supermarkets in Peru, Reuters Says

-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 
2011-10-21T11:30:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/chile-s-cencosud-to-open-25-supermarkets-in-peru-reuters-says.html
Cencosud SA,  Chile ’s largest
retailer by sales, plans to open 25 supermarkets in Peru within
the next year,  Reuters said .  Cencosud also expects to close the acquisition of Chilean
department store operator Johnson’s within the next 30 to 60
days, Cencosud chairman Horst Paulmann told reporters in Lima
yesterday, according to Reuters.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduardo Thomson in Santiago at 
